{"tid":409574,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Switch版DOOM實機試玩","createTime":"2017-09-22T07:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T13:12:40.000Z","uid":7371,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5da07a4224ab392b430c67fb03007de48d7adee4","tid":409574,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aY1OHwAqjME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaY1OHwAqjME&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNTwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=bbdea8e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aY1OHwAqjME</a><br />\n<br />\n畫面就幾正<br />\n即係2016年隻DOOM 4炒冷飯<br />\n有自動回血會易玩過DOOM 3好多<br />\n估唔到係手提機都玩到<br />\n聽聞話故事唔係咁掂<br />\nQ4 2017出<br />\n<br />\n遊戲內容有幾十GB<br />\n就算買實體版MP部份都係要dl先玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f15f1611a645925693e599b6c157f811340752","tid":409574,"uid":40310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"一出即買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116e36d49aa2be944bc642806079b9d1684648cf","tid":409574,"uid":119778,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"手提機玩返mario算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩乜鬼doom"},{"pid":"22a998d149fd28338b6460046289cf56fcfa8eb2","tid":409574,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手提機玩返mario算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩乜鬼doom</blockquote><br />\n你自己睇下段片堆外國玩家留言先啦<br />\n呢D game歐美好受落<br />\n<br />\nSwitch年尾出Biohazard Revelation兩集、Payday 2、LA Noire（查案但有槍戰）<br />\n下年出德軍總部2<br />\n<br />\n手提機開始會越黎越多槍game"},{"pid":"a066d4a326de142466e0c1ca69b7fea150c476ec","tid":409574,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"720p好撚正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" 