e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>pc一出就買左，的確好爽快好正<br />\n未玩可以考慮入手</blockquote><br />\n睇定d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻2k都lag機禁掣慢半秒</blockquote><br />\n難為你買埋d次等驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溝番條女未啊</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">not yet:</span>-(</blockquote><br />\n難怪你一日到黑上黎吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講事實咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a8ad5762f51682087df27622e0487d50cf38d9","tid":409574,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pc一出就買左，的確好爽快好正<br />\n未玩可以考慮入手</blockquote><br />\n睇定d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻2k都lag機禁掣慢半秒</blockquote><br />\n段片已經係手提實game gameplay<br />\n<br />\n總好過game show比你睇CG trailer<br />\n之後十幾年後先出到或取消左"},{"pid":"77798e0a277f36179adc2c49efcb8af60b0857e4","tid":409574,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"估唔到要有人嘈先多留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實段片都係比大家睇<br />\n手提機可以玩到2016年次世代DOOM呢類槍game<br />\n唔會畫質大縮水<br />\n<br />\n但個fd之前玩過<br />\n覺得呢隻有自動回血冇DOOM 3咁好<br />\n網上見故事都話唔掂<br />\n<br />\n自己打爆過DOOM 3故事都唔係好<br />\n但當年冇自動回血會怕死有時都刺激<br />\n去到地獄個關會沒收哂之前所有武器同彈藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前死慳埋成堆勁武器彈藥唔用會激到嘔血<br />\n<br />\n如你只係家打槍game<br />\n就梗係唔駛理Switch版啦"},{"pid":"50b8b2b1c98464cbb7ff283228c74567d2a395f9","tid":409574,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手提機玩返mario算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩乜鬼doom</blockquote><br />\n你自己睇下段片堆外國玩家留言先啦<br />\n呢D game歐美好受落<br />\n<br />\nSwitch年尾出Biohazard Revelation兩集、Payday 2、LA Noire（查案但有槍戰）<br />\n下年出德軍總部2<br />\n<br />\n手提機開始會越黎越多槍game</blockquote><br />\nPSP年代已經唔少啦<br />\n講到手提機玩FPS好突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}